#: includes/Admin.php:705
msgid "Uninstall behavior"
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin.php:707
msgid ""
"When this plugin is deleted from WordPress, it always removes its settings, "
"cached PDF files, and scheduled sync tasks. Invoice identifiers stored on "
"each order (B2Brouter invoice ID, invoice number, series code, and issue "
"date) are preserved by default so your tax audit trail stays intact."
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin.php:714
msgid "Also delete invoice identifiers from orders on uninstall"
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin.php:717
msgid ""
"Warning: this cannot be undone. Customer VAT / TIN numbers are never removed "
"by uninstall."
msgstr ""

