#: includes/Admin.php:840
msgid "Webhook Secret"
msgstr "Secret del webhook"

#: includes/Admin.php:850
msgid ""
"Enter the webhook secret from your B2Brouter dashboard to verify webhook "
"authenticity."
msgstr ""
"Introduïu el secret del webhook des del vostre panell de B2Brouter per "
"verificar l'autenticitat del webhook."

#: includes/Admin.php:858
msgid "Fallback Polling"
msgstr "Sondeig de reserva"

#: includes/Admin.php:868
msgid ""
"Keep polling as backup (checks every 6 hours if webhook fails). Recommended "
"for reliability."
msgstr ""
"Mantenir el sondeig com a reserva (verifica cada 6 hores si el webhook "
"falla). Recomanat per fiabilitat."

